# Tech stack defaults

Unless overridden in chat or repo docs:

| Layer | Choice |
|-------|--------|
| Backend | Python (FastAPI) |
| Queue | Redis |
| Database | PostgreSQL |
| Automation | Playwright |
| AI | Claude API (tool use + reasoning) |
| Voice | Vapi (fallback: Twilio) |
| Object storage | AWS S3 (or S3-compatible) |
| Secrets | AWS Secrets Manager |

Align new services and dependencies with these defaults when adding infrastructure.
